World day of fight against AIDS: to type foot, to sing, help
The Imbongi choral society repeats in Heidelberg, and the orphans of the AIDS of Swaziland are delighted by their arrival.
Here history of a bond which crosses much more than one distance of 8.733 kilometers.
Initially, foot is typed: the boots of cowboy, the tennis shoes, the pumps for the ladies and the moccasins for the men seek the rhythm by striking the ground of the foot. Very quickly, they find it.
One, two, three, four.
