It was with the power until 2003, his Ilham son succeeded to him thereafter.
At all events, the elderly people of Azerbaijan do not know the distress.
Mirzayeva monthly receives 230 manats (approximately the same amount as in euros) for its retirement, a sum which guarantees a good progress of life in the area.
